Macro replacement: GreaterThan_int32( Type.CalcCooldownDays( GetPlayer ), '(int32)0' )
Description: Does the activity type have a cooldown
Definition type: Global macro

Macro replacement: VariableSystem.HasValue( 'activity_locale_view', ViewVariable )
Description: Yields 'true' if there is NO activity event open and 'activity_locale_view' is set to the specified variable
Definition type: Global macro

Macro replacement: Or( Not( ActivityLogEntry.HasTag( 'crime' ) ), ObjectsEqual( ActivityLogEntry.GetCharacter, GetPlayer ) )
Description: Can the player see this log entry? Is the entry an intent entry, if it is: is the Character the local player?
Definition type: Global macro

-----------------------

IsContestFormatVersus
Macro replacement: Or( Or( Or( IsContestType( 'tournament_phase_joust' ) , IsContestType( 'tournament_phase_duel' ) ), IsContestType( 'tournament_phase_wrestling' ) ), IsContestType( 'tournament_phase_board_game' ) )
Description: Is the datacontexted contest a versus format contest?
Definition type: Global macro

Description: Is the specified view being displayed
Definition type: Global macro

-----------------------

Description: Does the datacontexted contest match the specified key?
Definition type: Global macro

-----------------------

IsDiarchyVisible
Macro replacement: Or( Character.HasActiveDiarchy, Character.IsDiarchOf( Character.GetLiege ) )
Description: Is diarchy button visible
Definition type: Global macro

-----------------------

IsFootContest
Macro replacement: Or( Or( Or( IsContestType( 'tournament_phase_joust' ), IsContestType( 'tournament_phase_melee' ) ), IsContestType( 'tournament_phase_wrestling' ) ), IsContestType( 'tournament_phase_duel' ) )
Description: Is the datacontexted contest a foot contest?
Definition type: Global macro

Description: Is the datacontexted contest a horse contest?
Definition type: Global macro
